message.entry: Specified measurement bands are outside the Nyquist interval [-Fs/2 Fs/2] if NormalizedFrequency is false, or [-1 1] if NormalizedFrequency is true.

Specified frequency resolution value is too large. The FrequencyResolution property should be < {0} {1}. Spectral estimates will be calculated with a single segment length equal to the data length. Note that the FrequencyResolution property has been set to the resolution value attained by this full-data segment length.

Specified frequency resolution is not attainable with the input data length. The FrequencyResolution property should be > {0} {1}. Spectral estimates will be calculated with a single segment length equal to the data length. Note that the FrequencyResolution property has been set to the resolution value attained by this full-data segment length.
